org.netlogo.extension.r
Class HoldRengineX

java.lang.Object
  org.netlogo.extension.r.HoldRengineX
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.nlogo.api.ExtensionManager
public class HoldRengineX
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.nlogo.api.ExtensionManager

Class to store the R connection and to transform data. Because NetLogo can't cast an Object stored in the ExtensionManager via ex.storeObject/ex.retrieveObject to classes and interfaces other than java natives and NetLogo ones, using NetLogo interfaces is one (dirty) way, to store the HoldRengineX object - containing the initialization of the jri-object with dynamic library loader.

Version:
0.3.3
Author:
JC Thiele
